title: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync
description: Bug 4121: JarExporter causes out of Sync (1GILQD5)
OB: When exporting a directory (project) and placing the exported jar in the same directory (project), an out of sync message is generated when overwriting the exported jar file for the second time.
EB: The exporting process should not include the exported jar file itself.
SR:
To reproduce:
1. Export a directory (project).
2. Place the exported jar file in the same directory (project).
3. Overwrite the exported jar file for the second time.
